<h1 id="digital-tools-for-workflow-and-project-management">Digital tools for workflow and project management</h1>

<p>This workshop will go over common digital tools that help with project management, task management, and collaboration.</p>

<p>This is a <a href="https://researchcommons.library.ubc.ca">UBC Library Research Commons workshop</a> and part of the Digital Toolkit series.</p>

<p>For more information about <a href="https://researchcommons.library.ubc.ca/events/">upcoming workshops</a> and to view <a href="https://researchcommons.library.ubc.ca/oer/">our open workshop content</a> find us at https://researchcommons.library.ubc.ca.</p>

<h2 id="goal-of-this-workshop">Goal of this workshop</h2>

<p>At the end of this workshop, you will be able to:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Identify a few common tools and what they are for.</li>
  <li>Articulate the big questions to ask when exploring a new tool.</li>
</ol>

<ul>
  <li>describe what web scraping is</li>
  <li>identify cases when web scraping may be useful</li>
  <li>use one method to scrape content from the web</li>
  <li>do basic cleaning on scraped output</li>
</ul>

